      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIGN ACTION (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (22.21) at this track behind My Machine in a NG. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Comes through a solid form race last start. Good form should continue. LAURIE'S RUPEE (1) has a strong record here with five wins and two placings from 13 starts. In the money last time at The Gardens (22.91) in a NG, finishing a 1.75 lengths second. Suited here and expected to run well. KENZIES COMET (6) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at The Gardens in a handy 15.78 beating Fireball Night. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Leading chance again. GINNY RIGGS (8) form at this distance reads well.",
